=Studyworx 3!
This is the latest version of StudyWorx designed to incorporate the new features of Rails 3.2.x.

My hope is to make this version more interactive and more friendly to a wider variety of devices.


==Goals:
* Implimentation of Rails 3.2.+ and HTML 5
* More friendly to small form factor devices
* Better communication features
  * This includes the addition of a User Profile page.
  * Personal, Team, and Public communication modes
* A flexible user team system.


